snippet: More than 20 musicians representing a variety of styles paired up with one another in a musical relay race of improvisation at the Brooklyn Masonic Temple.
abstract: Jon Pareles reviews concert featuring 20 musicians playing improvised round robin duets, presented by Red Bull Music Academy at Brooklyn Masonic Temple as part of Undead Music Festival.
lead_paragraph: More than 20 musicians representing a variety of styles paired up with one another in a musical relay race of improvisation at the Brooklyn Masonic Temple.
